      propertyPath: triggerEventsOnFirstInteractionOnly
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[0].defaultText
      value: It's Thursday! This is my desk!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[1].defaultText
      value: '**TURN OFF THE WATER** by finding and pressing the **RED BUTTON**'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[2].defaultText
      value: This isn't mandatory, but could you assist the other **3 ASSOCIATES**
        so I don't have to? You can find them littered across my desk.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[3].defaultText
      value: In any case, your **DEADLINE** is in 10 minutes.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: tertiaryDialogue.Array.data[0].defaultText
      value: Did you get enough sleep? You look rough, almost as bad as I do.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: secondaryDialogue.Array.data[0].defaultText
      value: The sooner you can **TURN OFF THE WATER**, the easier the day will get.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
