      propertyPath: objectiveToGive.Array.data[0]
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 365195395}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[0].defaultText
      value: Hey new guy! My name is **NPC 1**.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[1].defaultText
      value: I'm midway through covering one of **[color=#1FCD00]CARRIE'S[/color]**
        **ROUTINE** tasks. There's **4  STICKERS** left, can you help me find and
        collect them?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[2].defaultText
      value: Can you grab me a YELLOW PUSH-PIN?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: tertiaryDialogue.Array.data[0].defaultText
      value: Why am I still an **ASSOCIATE**? I've been here for six years and they
        still haven't given my own badge.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: secondaryDialogue.Array.data[0].defaultText
      value: Did you find all **4 STICKERS**?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
