      propertyPath: triggerEventsOnFirstInteractionOnly
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[0].defaultText
      value: Terry! I completely forgot about you. How's your week been going?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[1].defaultText
      value: Meet me at my desk tomorrow. In the meantime, go clock out for the day.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[2].defaultText
      value: In any case, your **DEADLINE** is in 10 minutes (600 seconds).
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[3].defaultText
      value: In any case, your **DEADLINE** is in 10 minutes (600 seconds).
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: tertiaryDialogue.Array.data[0].defaultText
      value: Hardly working or working hard? **haha**
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: secondaryDialogue.Array.data[0].defaultText
      value: Working hard or hardly working? **haha**
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
